text: Hi all. I am attempting to import a wordpress blog into HubSpot using Smart Copy. It says the import is completed and when I click review results it prompts me to Start Mapping. The problem I am having is when I click Start Mapping, it takes me to a blank white page devoid of content. Has anyone else had this problem? Anyone know of a fix?
